00:34:44,047 --> 00:34:47,909
client release. And this is something that is mandated as part of the milestone,

446
00:34:48,309 --> 00:34:50,371
and it's something that gets presented back to the team.

447
00:34:51,005 --> 00:34:54,248
in the spirit of iterative development, right?

448
00:34:54,368 --> 00:34:55,990
And we've instilled these processes,

