00:45:33,631 --> 00:45:40,577
mindset, align on shared goals. And it can be very, very simple. The best way to get past differences

597
00:45:40,657 --> 00:45:46,442
between the PM and their iterative mindset clashing with other big personalities on the

598
00:45:46,482 --> 00:45:53,107
dev team is to establish those shared goals. And you'll see that once you do that, magic starts

599
00:45:53,127 --> 00:45:54,148
happening with the rest of the team.

600
00:45:54,408 --> 00:45:58,632
You can start simple, like I said. Identify your North Star metrics that both creative and business

