00:46:11,564 --> 00:46:17,429
these, to run A-B tests and run experiments, and provide the communication to not only your

604
00:46:17,469 --> 00:46:19,571
internal dev team, but to outside stakeholders.

605
00:46:20,797 --> 00:46:25,461
in the form of air cover. The dev team will thank you because they'll be able to focus on creating great games.

